%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#1a1a2e', 'primaryTextColor': '#e0e0e0', 'lineColor': '#7f8c8d'}}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start[Task arrives] --> Q1{Risk score?}

    Q1 -->|0| DIRECT[DIRECT lane]
    Q1 -->|1-2| Q2{Files touched?}
    Q1 -->|3-5| Q3{Sensitive path?}
    Q1 -->|6+| HIGHRISK[FORCED HIGH-RISK]

    Q2 -->|≤3| FAST[FAST lane]
    Q2 -->|>3| STANDARD[STANDARD lane]

    Q3 -->|No| STANDARD
    Q3 -->|Yes| HIGHRISK

    HIGHRISK --> HR1[PLAN.md + ADR required]
    HR1 --> HR2[Reviewer required]
    HR2 --> HR3[Full test suite + SAST]
    HR3 --> HR4[Owner approval before merge]

    STANDARD --> S1[PLAN.md required]
    S1 --> S2[Full gate suite]
    S2 --> S3[Reviewer recommended]

    FAST --> F1[Inline plan]
    F1 --> F2[Per verification profile]
    F2 --> F3[Reviewer optional]

    DIRECT --> D1[Edit directly]
    D1 --> D2[Lint only]
    D2 --> D3[Commit]

    HR4 --> Merge[Merge / Release]
    S3 --> Merge
    F3 --> Merge
    D3 --> Merge
